data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Green Valley Ranch! This stunning 6-bedroom, 4-bathroom residence is a true gem that combines elegance, space, and convenience in one perfect package.
As you step inside, you'll immediately be greeted by the spacious and inviting living areas that offer ample room for both relaxation and entertainment. The open concept design allows for seamless flow throughout the main floor, providing a wonderful space for family gatherings and celebrations.
One of the standout features of this home is the luxurious 5-piece primary bath. Unwind in the spa-like oasis of the primary suite, complete with a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual vanities. It's your personal retreat where you can relax and rejuvenate after a long day.
This home is not only beautiful but also incredibly convenient. You'll love the easy access to grocery stores, just blocks away, making your daily shopping a breeze. Additionally, this property is a mere stone's throw from the airport, ensuring stress-free travel experiences. And for those seeking a bit of leisure, the world-renowned Gaylord Resort is just minutes away, offering endless entertainment options, dining, and relaxation.
Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a spacious and elegant 6-bedroom, 4-bathroom home in the highly sought-after Green Valley Ranch neighborhood. Schedule a viewing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort that this home has to offer. Your dream home awaits!
